This directory contains plugins for building a HTPC with the MediaBox framework.
These plugins are not intended for the maemo platform.

Start MediaBox like this to load the HTPC plugins:

  ./MediaBox.py --plugin-dir=components_htpc --blacklist-plugins=menu,media_viewer


Goals:

 - Remote control-driven UI (e.g. using AppleRemote or Nintendo Wiimote)
 - No keyboard or mouse ever required (those don't belong into a living-room)
 - DVD playback with navigatable DVD menus (using libxine)
 - Themable translucent OSD with compiz compositing
 - Fullscreen HD compatbility

